Jobsphere - Job Portal

ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

Jobsphere is a full-stack job portal that connects job seekers and employers, streamlining the recruitment process. The platform features role-based access for Jobseekers, Employers, and Admins, ensuring smooth operations, secure user authentication, and an efficient hiring experience.

ğŸš€ Features

ğŸ† Jobseekers

Register and create a profile with education and experience details.

Browse and apply for job postings.

Receive real-time employer response updates (Shortlisted, Pending, Rejected).

ğŸ¢ Employers

Register and create a company profile.

Post job openings with detailed descriptions and requirements.

View and manage job applications.

Shortlist, reject, or accept applications.

ğŸ”§ Admin

Monitor platform activity and manage employer accounts.

Remove inactive or fraudulent employers.

Maintain system security and oversee user authentication.

